  },
  "duration": 315.981,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In the year that king Uzziah died,",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.456,
      "end": 5.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw also the Lord sitting upon a throne,",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.747,
      "end": 7.512,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "high and lifted up,",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 7.692,
      "end": 9.782,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his train filled the temple.",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.962,
      "end": 19.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In the year that king Uzziah died, I saw also the Lord sitting upon a throne, high and lifted up, and his train filled the temple.",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 19.976,
      "end": 22.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Above it stood the seraphim;",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 22.432,
      "end": 24.429,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "each one had six wings;",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.609,
      "end": 27.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with twain he covered his face,",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 27.297,
      "end": 29.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with twain he covered his feet,",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 30.031,
      "end": 32.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with twain he did fly.",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 32.347,
      "end": 46.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Above it stood the seraphims: seraphim; each one had six wings; with twain he covered his face, and with twain he covered his feet, and with twain he did fly.",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 46.82,
      "end": 49.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And one cried unto another, and said:",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 49.647,
      "end": 54.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Holy, holy, holy, is the Lord of Hosts;",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 54.192,
      "end": 56.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the whole earth is full of his glory.",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 56.973,
      "end": 66.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And one cried unto another, and said: Holy, holy, holy, is the Lord of Hosts; the whole earth is full of his glory.",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 67.452,
      "end": 74.743,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the posts of the door moved at the voice of him that cried,",
      "verse": "16:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 74.923,
      "end": 77.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the house was filled with smoke.",
      "verse": "16:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 77.889,
      "end": 84.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the posts of the door moved at the voice of him that cried, and the house was filled with smoke.",
      "verse": "16:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 85.581,
      "end": 86.881,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then said I:",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 87.061,
      "end": 89.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wo is unto me! for I am undone;",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 90.167,
      "end": 92.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because I am a man of unclean lips;",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 93.087,
      "end": 96.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I dwell in the midst of a people of unclean lips;",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 97.122,
      "end": 100.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for mine eyes have seen the King, the Lord of Hosts.",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 101.064,
      "end": 117.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then said I: Woe Wo is unto me! for I am undone; because I am a man of unclean lips; and I dwell in the midst of a people of unclean lips; for mine eyes have seen the King, the Lord of Hosts.",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 118.416,
      "end": 120.877,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then flew one of the seraphim unto me,",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 121.057,
      "end": 123.472,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having a live coal in his hand,",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 123.652,
      "end": 127.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he had taken with the tongs from off the altar;",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 127.222,
      "end": 136.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then flew one of the seraphims seraphim unto me, having a live coal in his hand, which he had taken with the tongs from off the altar;",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 137.376,
      "end": 139.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he laid it upon my mouth, and said:",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 140.064,
      "end": 142.525,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Lo, this has touched thy lips;",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 142.705,
      "end": 145.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thine iniquity is taken away,",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 145.764,
      "end": 147.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and thy sin purged.",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 147.755,
      "end": 158.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he laid it upon my mouth, and said: Lo, this hath has touched thy lips; and thine iniquity is taken away, and thy sin purged.",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 159.116,
      "end": 161.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Also I heard the voice of the Lord, saying:",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 162.036,
      "end": 163.476,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whom shall I send,",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 163.656,
      "end": 165.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and who will go for us?",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 165.786,
      "end": 167.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then I said:",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 167.359,
      "end": 169.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Here am I; send me.",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 169.489,
      "end": 179.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Also I heard the voice of the Lord, saying: Whom shall I send, and who will go for us? Then I said: I, Here am I; send me.",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 180.014,
      "end": 181.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said:",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 181.587,
      "end": 186.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Go and tell this people\u2014",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 187.015,
      "end": 188.408,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Hear ye indeed,",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 188.588,
      "end": 190.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but they understood not;",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 190.626,
      "end": 192.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and see ye indeed,",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 192.478,
      "end": 194.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but they perceived not.",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 194.516,
      "end": 205.754,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said: Go and tell this people, Hear people--Hear ye indeed, but understand they understood not; and see ye indeed, but perceive they perceived not.",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 206.434,
      "end": 208.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Make the heart of this people fat,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 209.168,
      "end": 211.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and make their ears heavy,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 211.206,
      "end": 213.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shut their eyes\u2014",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 213.244,
      "end": 215.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest they see with their eyes,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 215.607,
      "end": 217.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hear with their ears,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 217.691,
      "end": 220.385,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and understand with their heart,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 220.565,
      "end": 223.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be converted and be healed.",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 223.531,
      "end": 239.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Make the heart of this people fat, and make their ears heavy, and shut their eyes; lest eyes--lest they see with their eyes, and hear with their ears, and understand with their heart, and convert, be converted and be healed.",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 240.093,
      "end": 241.393,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then said I:",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 241.573,
      "end": 243.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Lord, how long?",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 243.471,
      "end": 244.864,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said:",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 245.044,
      "end": 248.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Until the cities be wasted without inhabitant,",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 248.707,
      "end": 250.843,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the houses without man,",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 251.023,
      "end": 253.531,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the land be utterly desolate;",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 253.711,
      "end": 266.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then said I: Lord, how long? And he answered, said: Until the cities be wasted without inhabitant, and the houses without man, and the land be utterly desolate;",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 267.255,
      "end": 270.459,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord have removed men far away,",
      "verse": "16:12",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 270.639,
      "end": 275.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there shall be a great forsaking in the midst of the land.",
      "verse": "16:12",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 275.556,
      "end": 282.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord have removed men far away, and for there shall be a great forsaking in the midst of the land.",
      "verse": "16:12",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 283.481,
      "end": 286.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But yet there shall be a tenth,",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 286.262,
      "end": 287.934,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall return,",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 288.114,
      "end": 290.808,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall be eaten, as a teil tree,",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 290.988,
      "end": 296.329,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as an oak whose substance is in them when they cast their leaves;",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 296.509,
      "end": 299.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so the holy seed shall be the substance thereof.",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 299.94,
      "end": 315.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But yet in it there shall be a tenth, and it they shall return, and shall be eaten, as a teil tree, and as an oak whose substance is in them when they cast their leaves; so the holy seed shall be the substance thereof.",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 72
    }
  ]
}